SubjectAvoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income (Poland)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the Convention between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF POLAND for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME.
